{"sn35.157:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 35.157 ","sn35.157:0.2":"16. Nandikkhayavagga ","sn35.157:0.3":"Bahiranandikkhayasutta ","sn35.157:1.1":"“Anicceyeva, bhikkhave, bhikkhu rupe aniccati passati, sassa hoti sammaditthi. ","sn35.157:1.2":"Samma passam nibbindati. ","sn35.157:1.3":"Nandikkhaya ragakkhayo; ","sn35.157:1.4":"ragakkhaya nandikkhayo. ","sn35.157:1.5":"Nandiragakkhaya cittam suvimuttanti vuccati. ","sn35.157:1.6":"Anicceyeva, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sadde … ","sn35.157:1.7":"gandhe … ","sn35.157:1.8":"rase … ","sn35.157:1.9":"photthabbe … ","sn35.157:1.10":"dhamme aniccati passati, sassa hoti sammaditthi. ","sn35.157:1.11":"Samma passam nibbindati. ","sn35.157:1.12":"Nandikkhaya ragakkhayo; ","sn35.157:1.13":"ragakkhaya nandikkhayo. ","sn35.157:1.14":"Nandiragakkhaya cittam suvimuttanti vuccati”ti. ","sn35.157:1.15":"Dutiyam. "}